<view class="song-dynasty-page data-v-8163eeff"><view class="nav-bar data-v-8163eeff"><view class="back-btn data-v-8163eeff" bindtap="{{a}}"><text class="back-icon data-v-8163eeff">‹</text></view><text class="nav-title data-v-8163eeff">食在宋朝</text><view class="right-actions data-v-8163eeff"></view></view><scroll-view class="content-scroll data-v-8163eeff" scroll-y><view class="content-container data-v-8163eeff"><image class="main-image data-v-8163eeff" src="{{b}}" mode="aspectFill"/><view class="intro-section data-v-8163eeff"><text class="intro-title data-v-8163eeff">宋朝饮食文化</text><text class="intro-content data-v-8163eeff"> 宋朝是中国历史上饮食文化高度发展的时期。随着商品经济的繁荣和城市的发展，宋朝的饮食文化呈现出前所未有的繁荣景象。从宫廷到民间，从南方到北方，各地的饮食特色相互融合，形成了独特的宋代饮食文化。 </text></view><view class="feature-section data-v-8163eeff"><view class="feature-item data-v-8163eeff"><view class="feature-icon data-v-8163eeff">🍜</view><view class="feature-content data-v-8163eeff"><text class="feature-title data-v-8163eeff">面食文化</text><text class="feature-desc data-v-8163eeff">宋朝面食种类丰富，从简单的面条到精致的点心，体现了宋代饮食的精致化趋势。</text></view></view><view class="feature-item data-v-8163eeff"><view class="feature-icon data-v-8163eeff">🥘</view><view class="feature-content data-v-8163eeff"><text class="feature-title data-v-8163eeff">烹饪技法</text><text class="feature-desc data-v-8163eeff">宋代烹饪技法多样，炖、煮、蒸、炒、炸等技法已经相当成熟，为后世烹饪奠定了基础。</text></view></view><view class="feature-item data-v-8163eeff"><view class="feature-icon data-v-8163eeff">🍵</view><view class="feature-content data-v-8163eeff"><text class="feature-title data-v-8163eeff">茶文化</text><text class="feature-desc data-v-8163eeff">宋代茶文化达到高峰，点茶、斗茶等茶艺活动盛行，茶成为日常生活的重要组成部分。</text></view></view><view class="feature-item data-v-8163eeff"><view class="feature-icon data-v-8163eeff">🏮</view><view class="feature-content data-v-8163eeff"><text class="feature-title data-v-8163eeff">夜市文化</text><text class="feature-desc data-v-8163eeff">宋代夜市繁荣，各种小吃、饮品琳琅满目，形成了独特的夜市饮食文化。</text></view></view></view><view class="history-section data-v-8163eeff"><text class="section-title data-v-8163eeff">历史发展</text><view class="timeline data-v-8163eeff"><view class="timeline-item data-v-8163eeff"><text class="timeline-time data-v-8163eeff">北宋初期</text><text class="timeline-desc data-v-8163eeff">饮食文化承袭唐代，但开始出现新的变化，城市饮食业开始兴起。</text></view><view class="timeline-item data-v-8163eeff"><text class="timeline-time data-v-8163eeff">北宋中期</text><text class="timeline-desc data-v-8163eeff">饮食文化达到高峰，各种菜系形成，烹饪技法日趋成熟。</text></view><view class="timeline-item data-v-8163eeff"><text class="timeline-time data-v-8163eeff">南宋时期</text><text class="timeline-desc data-v-8163eeff">南方饮食文化进一步发展，形成了更加精致和多样化的饮食特色。</text></view></view></view></view></scroll-view></view>